{
  "stem": "10644.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my two soldiers had to push-- to push this car until it came out of trouble.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he brought me to a city called Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is-- it is-- it is-- it was quite a nice city in-- in the-- in the eastern part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is east of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- and he brought me to-- brought me to a big, open space.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I see there's a group of 30, 40 German officers, officers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some are officers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some are guests in SS uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I understand the day I see from the sign that they are all doctors or in, in the-- in the-- in the-- in the-- in health department.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came out of the wagon, and I saluted them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all 40, either by salute or by stretching the hand-- although he before told them that, that I am a Jew-- everybody saluted.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the attitude in '39.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In came a major and said, please--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A doctor, you know, maybe, you know, maybe the, the-- yes, for sure, you know, it was some, some respect in this-- in-- from this point of view.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- I-- with the same Volkswagen I was brought to the hospital in Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was told, you have to stay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stay there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got my, my small room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I started to work with wounded soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Germans, they were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in the city hospital of Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shortly, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was-- Siedlce was, at the beginning, was occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, you know, somehow on agreement with Russia, Siedlce has to belong to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So suddenly, the Germans moving out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they say to all doctors, personnel who wants to go to the west can go with us to the west.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And who wants to stay, will stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I stayed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And here the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But after four days, was already again a change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The, the Germans are coming again to Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there was a question of whether River Bug or River Wisla is a border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It is-- they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, [? because I informed ?] the-- they are coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, went to the director, I say, please, we have-- there were several hundred wounded.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From this several hundred, now we have around 30, 40, 40-- we-- enough still doctors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can I leave?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he say, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he allowed me to leave and to go to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bialystok was in the Russian hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to Bialystok, Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My, my, my my, parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- I stayed in, in Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was little afraid, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was all the time a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- belonged to Zionist's organization in the university.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very active summertime in the student's organization in Bialystok as a-- representing the Zionist people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now comes the communists.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now the leftist students who have a, a, a-- but it was--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Students?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're very, you know-- they're very with the Russians, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are all the communists, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they got positions right away, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, in general, they didn't do me any, any harm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will tell you the simple thing why.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the man who was the head of the remaining-- all the doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He is in Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He works in the-- in the administration-- health administration.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Jewish-- no, it was in the health administration of the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was an episode.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was in high school in Miedzyrzec-- Mezritch-- there was two other Jews, one Grinburg and one Kannel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kannel went to study medicine, I know, somewhere in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was not admitted to-- Grinburg went studying in Vilna-- I don't recall what.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he got involved, became a communist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was distributing on the street literature.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here, you know, Russian-- Polish police noticed him and started to chase.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the place where he could find it was just-- I am living not far away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came, ran to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- ran to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he tells me, I am running away from police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He is my friend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I worked with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I lived with him, work with him two years, you know, in, in, in duration.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- I, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I say, you stay in my room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where I could meet the leftist leaders over the Jewish students.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, please, Grinburg is in my apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They knew already everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
